These modes are different ways to view posts within a thread.  The user can set their own preference in their User CP.<br />
<br />
Threaded mode shows a tree of links to individual posts within the thread.  The tree shows the threading of the posts by indenting reply posts under the post they are in reply to.  Only one post is viewable at a time.<br />
<br />
Hybrid mode shows the threaded tree of post links as well as the linear expansion of those posts.